creator: PakZonIT
descriptionHtml:
Are you looking for an FPS shooting game with real gun shooting? You landed at the right game.

This commando game is going to train you to become a real shooter. FPS Game is about a shooter, who is out there hunting enemies with his shooting skills and collection of guns.

Ultra Commando gives you a chance to show your shooting skills and you can prove yourself to be a great shooter. The game is based on story modes with multiple levels, such as hostage rescue, saving military camps, bomb defusal and demolition. The FPS game offers you a variety of ways from where you can get rewards.

MULTIPLE CHALLENGING MISSIONS

FPS Shooting game has multiple challenging missions. All the fps missions will be unlocked once you finish the previous missions. Fps game is based on high end graphics which makes it feel like shooting in a real battlefield. The storyline described in this gun game is interconnected to each level.

MODERN WEAPONRY SELECTION

Ultra Commando game lets you play with a range of guns. You can upgrade your gun collection from the shop store. You can then play with guns such as, M9, MP-5, Snipers, AK-47, etc. An interesting feature is that you can carry two guns in the game. By using these guns, you can then shoot down your enemies with more precision and from a far distance.

STORYLINE BASED GAME LEVELS

FPS game comes with a story in every mission. Each game mission has several levels which are interconnected to each other. Instructions are given at every game level. Each level of game consists of different battle environments such as, different weather and terrains.

ENEMIES WITH SPECIALIZED TRAINING

FPS shooting game has been designed with highly trained commando enemies. This action & real game would let you polish your shooting skills. As the number of game level increase, you will encounter strong and trained enemies. Shooting experience at higher levels is interesting and challenging.

SEAMLESS GRAPHICS AND USER-FRIENDLY CONTROLS

Commando game has 3D graphics and action, which would feel like playing in a real battle ground. The game has user-friendly controls that are easy to use. The feature of Guns Auto-shooting when aiming at enemy makes it easy to fight opponents. FPS game has easy user interface and 3D game play features of Loading and changing guns, Maps to identify enemies, and intriguing sound effects.

ADDITIONAL FEATURES

• Remove Ads
• Quests having Special Rewards
• Game Statistics
• 50+ Levels
• Realistic Sound Effects
• Increase Health
• Enemy Mapping
